_sText:
Big spongebob prefab! i did use this for my 2 spongebob maps: gg_a$_spongebob and hosties_spongebob

Picture 1: in hammer
Picture 2: in-game normal
Picture 3: in-game with mat_wireframe 2 (so u can see the black shoes!)


INSTALLATION:

1. put the VTF and the VMT into your cstrike/material folder. (its important)
2. put the prefab_spongebob.vmf where u want!
3. open hammer and open the prefab.

If its good it will be appear good, if it got bug please PM or a feedback.



if you use this prefab in your map, give me some credits too!
